The evidence with the title 'Fact check: how much did the Modi government pay for the UPA era ... ' says Dec 6, 2018  ... BJP leaders said the Modi government repaid ₹ 1.5 lakh crore worth of oil  ... Not grow on trees & left unpaid bills of oil bonds worth rs . 1.3 lakh crore .  ... Claim : Modi government paid interest of ₹ 40,000 crore on oil bonds . 
